Here's another challenge: Smoke Strafe 'n Shoot

Prepare for close-quarters combat. Practice with the dummy movement set to constant strafe.

Play as Bangalore.

Equip any SMG, such as the CAR, R-99, or Volt, along with a 1x Digital Threat optic.

Deploy smoke at the location of the target dummy.

Engage the central dummy and eliminate it with full shields within one clip.
